managements discussion and analysis
j.p. morgan chase & co.
overview
j.p. morgan chase & co. is a leading
global financial services firm with assets
of $771billion and operations in more
than 50 countries. the firm serves more
than 30million consumers nationwide
through its retail businesses, and many of
the worlds most prominent corporate,
institutional and government clients
through its global wholesale businesses.
financial performance of jpmorgan chase
as of or for the year ended december 31,
(in millions, except per share and ratio data)
