business outlook
in 2004, the composition of ibs revenues
is expected to change. growth in
client-related revenue may be offset by
potentially lower securities gains and nii. nii may be lower
due to decreased spreads on investment
securities and lower loan volumes. the ib credit
outlook is stable, although credit costs
may be higher than the unusually low
levels seen in 2003.
