nm-
because the minimum and maximum may occur on different days for different
risk components, it is not meaningful to compute a portfolio diversification
effect. in addition, jpmorgan chases average and period-end vars are less than
the sum of the vars of its market risk components, due to risk offsets
resulting from portfolio diversification.
